  "title": "Logistics & Operations Specialist (Forklift Driver)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title: Logistics & Operations Specialist (Forklift Driver)</strong></p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Tuas, Singapore<br /><em>Free daily shuttle bus from Choa Chu Kang & Joo Koon MRT stations.</em></p><ul><li><p>Receive, inspect, and accurately store incoming goods.</p></li><li><p>Prepare finished products for on-time dispatch.</p></li><li><p>Safely operate forklifts (counterbalance/reach truck) to move materials.</p></li><li><p>Perform regular inventory counts and maintain precise digital records.</p></li><li><p>Assist with loading/unloading trucks and organizing the warehouse space.</p></li><li><p>Strictly follow all safety protocols and maintain a clean workspace.</p></li><li><p>Support production teams with timely material supply.</p></li><li><p>Report any equipment issues or inventory discrepancies immediately.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>A <strong>valid Forklift License</strong> (experience with counterbalance/reach trucks is a plus).</p></li><li><p>Willingness to work on a <strong>rotating shift pattern</strong> (you can state your preference for a fixed day or night shift).</p></li></ul><p><strong></strong></p><p><strong>Compensation:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Basic Salary:</strong> From $2,300/month.</p></li><li><p><strong>Gross Monthly Potential:</strong> $2,300 – $3,300, based on your chosen 4, 5, or 6-day work week.</p></li><li><p><strong>Monthly Allowances (Up to ~$400):</strong></p><ul><li><p>Shift Allowance: $8 (Day) / $18 (Night) per shift</p></li><li><p>Extra Daily Bonus: $3</p></li><li><p>Transport Allowance: $4 per day</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Annual Bonuses:</strong> Performance Bonus (1-2 months) + 13th Month Salary.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Work-Life Balance:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Your Choice of Shift:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Day Shift: 7:30 AM – 7:30 PM</p></li><li><p>Night Shift: 7:30 PM – 7:30 AM</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Overtime pay available for extra hours.</p></li><li><p><strong>Affordable Meals:</strong> Company canteen with meals from $2-$3.</p></li><li><p><strong>Fully Equipped:</strong> All necessary safety gear (PPE) provided.</p></li><li><p><strong>Time Off:</strong> 11 days of annual leave to start.</p></li><li><p><strong>Grow With Us:</strong> Clear opportunities for career development.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
